  "prompt": "Who provides the best Digital Marketing Classes in Pune?",
  "response": "While I can't provide real-time recommendations, as of my last update, several institutions in Pune are well-known for offering quality digital marketing classes. Here are some of them:\n\n1. **Digital Marketing Courses by KRB** - Known for a comprehensive curriculum that covers various aspects of digital marketing.\n\n2. **NIIT** - Offers structured courses with a focus on practical knowledge and hands-on experience.\n\n3. **MCTA (Maharashtra Certified Trainers Academy)** - Offers various digital marketing courses with a good balance of theory and practical training.\n\n4. **Edureka** - An online and physical presence, Edureka is known for their live instructor-led sessions and a hands-on approach.\n\n5. **IIDE (Indian Institute of Digital Education)** - Offers a range of courses in digital marketing and is known for its practical approach.\n\n6. **Think Digital Academy** - Focuses on practical sessions along with theoretical knowledge, providing case studies and real-world examples.\n\n7. **UpGrad** - Partners with universities for professional courses, including digital marketing.\n\nWhen looking for the best classes, consider checking reviews, course content, faculty qualifications, and whether they offer hands-on projects. It's also a good idea to attend a demo class if possible before enrolling.",
